data.description: This charming townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entry, experience the welcoming ambiance of a spacious yet cozy 4-bedroom layout. The open-concept kitchen serves as a focal point, perfect for entertaining or enjoying family meals, with a generous island for seating. For convenience and hospitality, a full bedroom and bathroom on the ground floor ensure privacy for guests or those preferring first-floor accommodations. Upstairs, three additional bedrooms and a well-appointed full bathroom await. The true gem of the upper level is the luxurious primary suite, boasting vaulted ceilings for added grandeur. The primary bathroom is a relaxing retreat with a separate shower and tub for indulgent bathing, complemented by dual sinks for convenience. But perhaps the most impressive feature is the primary suite's thoughtfully designed custom closet, offering ample space and organization options. This townhome is truly a must-see!
